videos.description: DeShone Kizer connects with Equanimeous St. Brown on a 13-yard touchdown to give Notre Dame an early lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Kizer's pass to Brown gives Notre Dame early lead

videos.description: Shane Buechele throws his first career touchdown pass for Texas with a 19-yard strike to Armanti Foreman to tie the Longhorns' game against Notre Dame at seven.

videos.description: After throwing a touchdown pass earlier in the game, Shane Buechele keeps it himself for the one-yard touchdown to give Texas a 14-7 lead over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Buechele keeps it himself to give Texas a lead

videos.description: DeShone Kizer pass complete to Torii Hunter Jr. for 19 yds to the NDame 44 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Torii Hunter Sr. cheering on his son Torri Hunter Jr.

videos.description: DeShone Kizer passes once again to Equanimeous St. Brown, who gets hit but manages to flip forward into the end zone for the 30-yard touchdown to tie Notre Dame's game with Texas at 14.
videos.headline: St. Brown flips into end zone to tie it for Notre Dame

videos.description: Shane Buechele pass complete to Jerrod Heard for 68 yds to the NDame 1 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: S. Buechele pass,to J. Heard for 68 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Tyrone Swoopes runs 1 yard for a touchdown to put Texas up 21-14
videos.headline: Swoopes gives Texas the lead

videos.description: Notre Dame quarterback Malik Zaire throws the ball away and a man on the sideline cannot protect himself in time before it hits him in the face.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Man on Texas sideline gets hit in the face) 2016/09/04

videos.headline: Man on Texas sideline gets hit in the face

videos.description: Tyrone Swoopes rushes to the outside and scores on the one-yard touchdown to give Texas a 21-14 lead, but the camera operator is an unfortunate spectator as Swoopes accidentally takes him out on the play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Swoopes runs outside, takes out cameraman to give Texas lead) 2016/09/04

videos.headline: Swoopes runs outside, takes out cameraman to give Texas lead

videos.description: Shane Buechele pass complete to John Burt for 72 yds for a TD
videos.headline: S. Buechele pass,to J. Burt for 72 yds for a TD

videos.description: Malik Zaire sacked by Kevin Vaccaro for a loss of 11 yards to the NDame 20
videos.headline: Vaccaro goes airborne to sack Notre Dame QB

videos.description: Less than a minute into the second half, Shane Buechele connects with John Burt on a 72-yard touchdown pass to give Texas a 28-14 lead over Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Buechele goes deep to increase Texas' lead in second half) 2016/09/04

videos.headline: Buechele goes deep to increase Texas' lead in second half

videos.description: DeShone Kizer run for 29 yds for a TD (Justin Yoon KICK)
videos.headline: Kizer rolls into the end zone for Notre Dame

videos.description: Capitalizing off an interception by their defense, Notre Dame gets within three points of Texas when DeShone Kizer connects with Torii Hunter Jr. in the end zone for a five-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kizer finds Hunter Jr. in end zone to get Notre Dame close

videos.description: Justin Yoon 36-yard field goal is BLOCKED by Naashon Hughes
videos.headline: Texas blocks Notre Dame's game-tying FG attempt

videos.description: DeShone Kizer completes a 17-yard touchdown pass to Josh Adams to give Notre Dame a 35-31 lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Notre Dame takes the lead with the touchdown pass to Josh Adams

videos.description: Notre Dame wide receiver Torii Hunter Jr. tries to catch a touchdown pass, but the ball is jarred loose after a big high hit to the helmet, causing him to leave the game. Hunter's family goes to the locker room to check on him.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Torii Hunter Jr. gets knocked out of game on controversial hit) 2016/09/04

videos.headline: Torii Hunter Jr. gets knocked out of game on controversial hit

videos.description: D'Onta Foreman gets the handoff and rushes by the Notre Dame defense for the 19-yard touchdown to give Texas a 37-35 lead over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Texas takes late lead on Foreman TD

videos.description: Texas attempts to gain a three-point lead over Notre Dame, but the blocked PAT is returned the other way to give the Fighting Irish two points and a 37-37 tie.
videos.headline: Notre Dame stuns Texas by returning blocked PAT to tie game

videos.description: D'Onta Foreman scores a 19-yard rushing touchdown for Texas to give them a lead, but it is short-lived as Notre Dame blocks the extra point and returns it for the defensive two-point conversion to tie the game at 37.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas gets the late TD, but Notre Dame capitalizes on the PAT) 2016/09/04

videos.headline: Texas gets the late TD, but Notre Dame blocks and returns the PAT

videos.description: Tyrone Swoopes run for 3 yds for a TD
videos.headline: T. Swoopes run for 3 yds for a TD in overtime

videos.description: Needing a touchdown to tie it in the first overtime, DeShone Kizer passes to C.J. Sanders, who finds the end zone for the 25-yard touchdown, sending the game to a second overtime.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's TD sends game to second overtime

videos.description: Justin Yoon 39 yd FG GOOD
videos.headline: J. Yoon 39 yd FG GOOD to take lead in 2nd Overtime

videos.description: Tyrone Swoopes run for 11 yds to the NDame 5 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: T. Swoopes fighting the Irish for the first down

videos.description: Tyrone Swoopes powers through the Notre Dame defense and dives into the end zone for the touchdown to give Texas a 50-47 victory over Notre Dame in two overtimes.
videos.headline: Swoopes dives into the end zone to gives Texas the win in 2OT

videos.description: Tyrone Swoopes powers his way through Notre Dame's defense for a 6-yard touchdown that gives Texas a 50-47 victory in double overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Swoopes' diving TD wins 2OT thriller for Texas) 2016/09/04

videos.headline: Swoopes' diving TD wins 2OT thriller for Texas

videos.description: Charlie Strong talks about Texas' thrilling 50-47 double-overtime win over No. 10 Notre Dame and how impressed he was with both Tyrone Swoopes and Shane Buechele.
